      <p>Yes. You can select one of our premium gift card designs during checkout and add your own personalized message.</p>

      <h3 style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--gold-dark); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">How it Works</h3>
      <p>We offer a built-in greeting card customizer that lets you design a personalized card to accompany your candle order. You can select one of our premium card templates, add custom text messages with adjustable fonts, sizes, and colors, and drag decorative stickers anywhere on the canvas.</p>
      
